<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1945-03-06T07:35:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1945-03-06T07:35:00-05:00" n="329" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d329">
                            <note rend="inline" type="source">761.91/3–645: Telegram</note>
                            <head>
                                <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in Iran</hi> (<persName type="from"><hi rend="italic">Morris</hi></persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                                </hi>
                            </head>
                            <opener>
                                <dateline rendition="#right">
                                    <placeName>
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Tehran</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1945-03-06T16:00:00+03:25">March
                                        6, 1945—4 p.m.</date>
                                    <lb/> [Received March 6—3:21 p.m.]</dateline>
                            </opener>
                            <p>154. Foreign Minister Entezam, who seemed much worried, told me last
                                night that Molotov in his latest interview with Iranian Ambassador
                                Ahy, had pointedly renewed Soviet complaint against asserted
                                anti-Russian attitude of Iranian Government. Molotov made special
                                reference to law forbidding oil concessions and said Soviets were
                                holding it against Iran. This interview was subsequent to Yalta
                                Conference.</p>
                            <closer>
                                <signed>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Morris</hi>
                                </signed>
                            </closer>
                        </div>
                        </body></text></TEI>